<body>
<div class="content" style="padding-top:20px;">
  <div class="main">
    <div class="leftx">
      <div class="main_content">
        <h2 class="title4">支付宝 创建二维码及上传流程</h2>
        <p></p>
		<p style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;white-space: normal"><span style="font-size: 21px;font-family: 宋体">第一步打开手机支付宝找到收款</span></p>
		<p style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;white-space: normal"><span style="font-size: 21px"><img width="250" height="442" src="images/1.jpg"></span></p>
		<p style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;white-space: normal"><span style="font-size: 21px"><img width="250" height="442" src="images/2.jpg" /></span></p>
		
		<p style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;white-space: normal"><span style="font-size: 21px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;white-space: normal"><span style="font-size: 21px;font-family: 宋体">第二步进入收款按钮设置金额</span></p>
		
		<p style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;white-space: normal"><span style="font-size: 21px"><img width="254" height="450" src="images/3.jpg"></span></p><p style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;white-space: normal"><span style="font-size: 21px">&nbsp;</span></p>
		
		<p style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;white-space: normal"><span style="font-size: 21px;font-family: 宋体">新版本支付宝APP</span></p>
		
		<p style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;white-space: normal"><span style="font-size: 21px"><img width="252" height="389" src="images/new001.jpg"></span></p>
		<p style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;white-space: normal"><span style="font-size: 21px">&nbsp;</span></p>
		
				<p style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;white-space: normal"><span style="font-size: 21px"><img width="252" height="450" src="images/new002.jpg"></span></p>
		<p style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;white-space: normal"><span style="font-size: 21px">&nbsp;</span></p>
		
		<p style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;white-space: normal"><span style="font-size: 21px;font-family: 宋体">第三步设置金额</span></p>
		<p align="center"><span style="font-size: 21px;font-family: 宋体">支付宝二维码生成设置金额</span></p>
		
						<p style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;white-space: normal"><span style="font-size: 21px"><img width="252" height="450" src="images/new003.jpg"></span></p>
		<p style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;white-space: normal"><span style="font-size: 21px">&nbsp;</span></p>
		
		<p style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;white-space: normal"><span style="font-size: 21px;font-family: 宋体">例如：</span><span style="font-size: 21px">1</span><span style="font-size: 21px;font-family: 宋体">元分组</span></p>
        <p style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: 'Times New Roman';white-space: normal"><span class="STYLE1">1.01</span></p>
        <p class="STYLE2" style=";text-align: center;font-size: 21px;font-family: 'Times New Roman';white-space: normal"><span style="font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;">1.02</span></p>
        <p class="STYLE2" style=";text-align: center;font-size: 21px;font-family: 'Times New Roman';white-space: normal"><span style="font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;">1.03</span></p>
        <p class="STYLE2" style=";text-align: center;font-size: 21px;font-family: 'Times New Roman';white-space: normal"><span style="font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;">1.04</span></p>
        <p class="STYLE2" style=";text-align: center;font-size: 21px;font-family: 'Times New Roman';white-space: normal"><span style="font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;">1.05</span></p>
        <p class="STYLE2" style=";text-align: center;font-size: 21px;font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;;white-space: normal">...</p>
        <p class="STYLE2" style=";text-align: center;font-size: 21px;font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;;white-space: normal">1.09</p>
        <p style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: 'Times New Roman';white-space: normal">每组最大到09，一般收款不是很频繁正常设置到05就可以了</p>
        <p style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: 'Times New Roman';white-space: normal"><span style="font-size: 21px;font-family: 宋体">例如：</span><span style="font-size: 21px">10</span><span style="font-size: 21px;font-family: 宋体">元分组</span></p>
        <p style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: 'Times New Roman';white-space: normal"><span class="STYLE1">10.01</span></p>
        <p style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: 'Times New Roman';white-space: normal"><span class="STYLE1">10.02</span></p>
        <p style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: 'Times New Roman';white-space: normal"><span class="STYLE1">10.0</span><span class="STYLE1">3</span></p>
        <p style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: 'Times New Roman';white-space: normal"><span class="STYLE2" style=";text-align: center;font-size: 21px;font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;;white-space: normal">...</span></p>
        <p class="STYLE2" style=";text-align: center;font-size: 21px;font-family: 'Times New Roman';white-space: normal"><span style="font-family: &quot;宋体&quot;">10.09</span></p>
        <p align="center"><span style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: 'Times New Roman';white-space: normal"><span style="font-size: 21px;font-family: 宋体">把生成好的二维码截屏发送到电脑进行下一步处理</span></span></p>

		<p style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: 'Times New Roman';white-space: normal"><span style="font-size: 21px;font-family: 宋体">继续往下看</span><span style="font-size: 21px">&nbsp;</span></p>
		<p style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;white-space: normal"><span style="font-size: 21px;font-family: 宋体">第四步、将生成好的二维码截屏保存到手机里</span></p>
		<p style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;white-space: normal"><span style="font-size: 21px"><img width="252" height="450" src="images/new003.jpg"></span></p>
		<p style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;white-space: normal"><span style="font-size: 21px">&nbsp;</span></p>
		<p style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;white-space: normal"><span style="font-size: 21px;font-family: 宋体">第五步、将生成好的二维码全部发送到</span><span style="font-size: 21px">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 21px;font-family: 宋体">电脑（电脑登陆好你的QQ），我做演示共做了5个支付宝1元组的二维码，一起发送到电脑。</p>
		<p style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;white-space: normal"><span style="font-size: 21px"><img width="264" height="469" src="images/6.jpg">&nbsp;<img width="263" height="471" src="images/7.jpg"></span></p>
		<p style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;white-space: normal"><span style="font-size: 21px">&nbsp;</span></p><p style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;white-space: normal"><span style="font-size: 21px;font-family: 宋体">第六步、将二维码另存为到文件夹</span></p><p style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: 'Times New Roman';white-space: normal"><img src="images/9.jpg" width="407" height="480" /></p>
		<p style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;white-space: normal"><span style="font-size: 21px;font-family: 宋体">例如这</span><span style="font-size: 21px">5</span><span style="font-size: 21px;font-family: 宋体">个</span><span style="font-size: 21px">1</span><span style="font-size: 21px;font-family: 宋体">元二维码</span></p>
		<p style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: 'Times New Roman';white-space: normal"><img src="images/8.jpg" width="753" height="359" /></p>
		<p style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;white-space: normal"><span style="font-size: 21px;font-family: 宋体">第七步 处理二维码</span></p>
		<p style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;white-space: normal"><span class="STYLE1">用QQ截图 截下二维码后保存对应文件名称待用</span></p>
		<p style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;white-space: normal"><img src="images/10.jpg" width="751" height="399" /></p>
		<p style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;white-space: normal">比如这个1元组二维码，把二维码剪切下来保存文件名对应二维码的备注，这个保存为1.01.jpg依此类推。</p>
		<p style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;white-space: normal"><span class="STYLE1">下图是已经截好的五个二维码图片</span></p>
		<p style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;white-space: normal"><img src="images/11.jpg" width="816" height="374" /></p>
		<p style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;white-space: normal"><span style="font-size: 21px;font-family: 宋体">第七步：登陆二维码管理系统上传二维码</span></p>
		<p style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;white-space: normal"><img src="images/12.jpg" width="874" height="294" /></p>
		<p align="center" style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; white-space: normal;"><span style="font-size: 21px;font-family: 宋体"><img src="images/13.jpg" width="878" height="275" /><br></span><img src="images/14.jpg" width="716" height="372" /></p>
		<p style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;white-space: normal"><span style="font-size: 21px;font-family: 宋体">点击进入</span><span style="font-size: 21px">支付宝1</span><span style="font-size: 21px;font-family: 宋体">元二维码管理</span></p>
		<p style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;white-space: normal"><img src="images/15.jpg" width="776" height="285" /></p>
		<p style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;white-space: normal"><img src="images/16.jpg" width="775" height="306" /></p>
		<p style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: 'Times New Roman';white-space: normal"><img src="images/new004.jpg" width="865" height="472" /></p>
		<p style="font-size: 14px; font-family: 'Times New Roman'; white-space: normal; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 21px">二维码备注和当前建立的 理由必须保持一致，否则将不能到账。</span></p>
		<p style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: 'Times New Roman';white-space: normal"><span style="font-size: 21px"><img width="523" height="252" src="images/1468032994705549.jpg"></span></p>
		<p style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;white-space: normal"><span style="font-size: 21px;font-family: 宋体">一个金额组</span><span style="font-size: 21px">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 21px;font-family: 宋体">至少要建立</span><span style="font-size: 21px">5</span><span style="font-size: 21px;font-family: 宋体">个二维码</span><span style="font-size: 21px">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 21px;font-family: 宋体">备注不能相同，在上传二维码时候备注信息必须和当前二维码一致否则充值将不能到账</span></p>
		<p style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;white-space: normal"><img src="images/new005.jpg" width="788" height="483" /></p>
		<p style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: &#39;Times New Roman&#39;;white-space: normal">上传好了5个1元组的二维码的效果，备注理由要按照顺序填加。</p>
		<p style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: 'Times New Roman';white-space: normal">实际使用每组二维码最好多建立些，建议支付宝每组至少5个。</p>
		<p style=";text-align: center;font-size: 14px;font-family: 'Times New Roman';white-space: normal">本例有演示视频，可以观看演示视频。</p>
		<p><br></p><p></p>
      </div>
    </div>
   
    <div class="clear"></div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="foot"><br>
  <div class="clear"></div>
</div>
